<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-10747] CQL.textile syntax incorrectly includes optional keyspace for aggregate SFUNC and FINALFUNC</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10747</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/doc/cql3/CQL.textile&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CQL.textile&lt;/a&gt; incorrectly includes an optional keyspace for the &lt;tt&gt;SFUNC&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;FINALFUNC&lt;/tt&gt; parts of a &lt;tt&gt;CREATE AGGREGATE&lt;/tt&gt; statement.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The grammar for 2.2 and 3.0 does not allow a keyspace to be specified here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the CQL.textile:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&amp;lt;create-aggregate-stmt&amp;gt; ::= CREATE ( OR REPLACE )? 
                            AGGREGATE ( IF NOT EXISTS )?
                            ( &amp;lt;keyspace&amp;gt; &apos;.&apos; )? &amp;lt;aggregate-name&amp;gt;
                            &apos;(&apos; &amp;lt;arg-type&amp;gt; ( &apos;,&apos; &amp;lt;arg-type&amp;gt; )* &apos;)&apos;
                            SFUNC ( &amp;lt;keyspace&amp;gt; &apos;.&apos; )? &amp;lt;state-functionname&amp;gt;
                            STYPE &amp;lt;state-type&amp;gt;
                            ( FINALFUNC ( &amp;lt;keyspace&amp;gt; &apos;.&apos; )? &amp;lt;final-functionname&amp;gt; )?
                            ( INITCOND &amp;lt;init-cond&amp;gt; )?
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
